cs.CL, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.PL, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and code generation. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses generating code in programming languages. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper presents a neural model for generating code. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with generating code in programming languages and discusses the syntax of programming languages. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper presents a new approach to generating code using structural language modeling.
